<docbook><section><title>ProgessDriverUnicodeConfig</title><bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h2">Configure Progress For Unicode Support</bridgehead>
<para>For ESQL-92 clients the internal codepage is determined by the value of the client&#39;s SQL_CLIENT_CHARSET environment variable, if set.
 Otherwise, the internal codepage is that of the client&#39;s locale.
 There is a similar environment variable that controls the codepage of messages sent by the database server.</para><para>See Also: <ulink url="ProgressUnicodeConfig">ProgressUnicodeConfig</ulink> </para></section></docbook>